      <title>法国国有投资公司考虑入股赛诺菲消费品部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/french-investment-firm-eyes-stake-in-sanofi-consumer-health-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Bpifrance SACA 执行董事 Jose Gonzalo 称，Bpifrance SACA 正在考虑对 Sanofi SA 的消费者健康部门进行投资，因为它着眼于更大的健康投资。]]></description>
