      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:45:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莱恩称欧洲央行仍对国内通胀有所担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/lane-says-ecb-still-has-some-concerns-about-domestic-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧洲央行并不完全相信欧元区产生的价格压力得到充分控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/lane-says-ecb-still-has-some-concerns-about-domestic-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
